Package spring.service

Class DevelopmentService

  • java.lang.Object
    • spring.service.DevelopmentService
  • @Service("developmentService")
public class DevelopmentService
extends java.lang.Object
    Service for handling all requests related to Developments. Maintains a proxy of Developments for each session.
    Author:
    Shane Lockwood

      • loadByPage

        public Proxy<Development> loadByPage​(java.lang.String sessionId,
                                     java.util.Set<Development> developments,
                                     int page)
        Proxies the passed Developments with the passed page and returns the Proxy. The proxied data is sorted with DevelopmentComparatorByVote.
        Parameters:
        sessionId - The String representing the session's id.
        developments - The Developments to be proxied.
        page - The int representing the subset of data to be stored in the Proxy.
        Returns:
        Proxy
